## 2. Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["🌐 Target URL(s)"] --> B["Module 01: DOM Crawler<br/>(Cypress + JS)"]
    B --> C["Module 02: Scenario Generator<br/>(Rule Engine + Integration Engine)"]
    C --> D["🔘 Approval Gate<br/>(Human-in-the-Loop)"]
    D --> E["Module 03: Risk Engine<br/>(Scorer + CI Predictor)"]
    E --> F["Module 04: Test Code Generator<br/>(CypressBuilder)"]
    F --> G["Module 11: Regression Optimizer<br/>(Smart Pruning)"]
    G --> H["Module 05: Cypress Executor<br/>(Batched + Retry)"]
    H --> I["Module 09: Self-Healing<br/>(Fallback Selector Learning)"]
    I --> H
    H --> J["Module 06: Flakiness Detector"]
    H --> K["Module 07: API Anomaly Detector"]
    H --> L["Module 08: Visual Regression<br/>(OpenCV + SSIM)"]
    H --> M["Module 10: CI Predictor<br/>(Random Forest ML)"]
    J --> N["📊 Streamlit Dashboard<br/>(7 Analytics Tabs)"]
    K --> N
    L --> N
    M --> N
```

### Data Flow

```
URL Input → Cypress Crawler → DOM JSON → Rule Engine → Scenarios JSON
    → Approval Gate → Risk Scoring → Cypress .cy.js Generation
    → Batched Execution → Self-Healing Loop → Results JSON
    → Flakiness + Anomaly + Visual Analysis → Dashboard
```

