## 4. Pipeline Flow

The agent executes a **6-step pipeline**, orchestrated by [agent/agent_runner.py](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/agent/agent_runner.py):

| Step | Module(s) | Description |
|------|-----------|-------------|
| **Step 1** | DOM Crawler (01) | Cypress visits URL, extracts interactive DOM elements |
| **Step 2** | Scenario Generator (02) + Regression Optimizer (11) | Rule engine creates test scenarios; optimizer prunes stable ones |
| **Step 3** | Risk Engine (03) + CI Predictor (10) | Scores & prioritizes tests by historical failure rate + ML prediction |
| **Step 4** | Test Code Generator (04) | Generates [.cy.js](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/cypress/e2e/crawler.cy.js) Cypress spec files from prioritized plan |
| **Step 5** | Executor (05) + Self-Healer (09) | Runs tests with 3-retry loop; healer learns fallback selectors |
| **Step 5.5** | Visual Regression (08) | Captures & compares screenshots with SSIM + OpenCV |
| **Step 6** | Flakiness (06) + Anomaly (07) | Statistical analysis of pass/fail variance + execution time anomalies |

