## 5. Module 01 — DOM Crawler

> **Files:** [cypress/e2e/crawler.cy.js](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/cypress/e2e/crawler.cy.js) + [modules/01_dom_crawler/dom_parser.py](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/01_dom_crawler/dom_parser.py)

### Design

The crawler is a **two-component system**: a Cypress spec that runs inside a real browser, and a Python parser that cleans the extracted data.

### Cypress Crawler ([crawler.cy.js](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/cypress/e2e/crawler.cy.js) — 238 lines)

**5-Phase Extraction Pipeline:**

| Phase | Purpose | Key Technique |
|-------|---------|---------------|
| **Phase 1** | Auto-dismiss cookie/GDPR banners | Multi-strategy: text matching (40+ consent phrases in 4 languages), OneTrust, CookieBot, Quantcast, TrustArc handlers |
| **Phase 2** | Remove blocking overlays/modals/iframes | DOM removal of fixed/sticky/absolute positioned consent elements; restores `body.overflow` |
| **Phase 3** | Detect bot protection (Cloudflare, CAPTCHA) | Text-based detection of 12+ bot indicators; flags output JSON |
| **Phase 4** | Scroll & lazy-load trigger | `cy.scrollTo('bottom')` to force lazy-loaded elements |
| **Phase 5** | Extract interactive elements | `querySelectorAll('input, button, a[href], select, textarea, form')` |

**Key Functions:**
- Spoofs `User-Agent` header to mimic real Chrome browser
- Captures: tag, id, classes, type, name, href, text, visibility
- Saves via `cy.task('saveDomData', ...)` to `data/{run_id}.json`

### DOM Parser ([dom_parser.py](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/01_dom_crawler/dom_parser.py) — 64 lines)

**Class:** [DOMParser](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/01_dom_crawler/dom_parser.py#5-56)

| Method | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| [parse_dom(filename)](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/01_dom_crawler/dom_parser.py#10-56) | Loads JSON, filters bot artifacts, counts forms/buttons |

**Key Logic:**
- Filters hidden elements (`isVisible == False`)
- Removes known bot-protection artifacts (cloudflare, turnstile, captcha, hcaptcha, recaptcha)
- Returns structured dict: `{ url, interactive_elements, forms_found, buttons_found, bot_protection_detected }`

