## 6. Module 02 — Scenario Generator

> **Files:** [modules/02_scenario_generator/rule_engine.py](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/02_scenario_generator/rule_engine.py) + [integration_engine.py](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/02_scenario_generator/integration_engine.py)

### Rule Engine ([rule_engine.py](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/02_scenario_generator/rule_engine.py) — 248 lines)

**Class:** [RuleEngine](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/02_scenario_generator/rule_engine.py#6-244)

Dynamically generates up to **70 test scenarios** across **6 tiers** from crawled DOM data.

| Tier | Test IDs | Max Cap | What It Tests |
|------|----------|---------|---------------|
| **Tier 1: Form Validation** | `TC_FORM_POS_*`, `TC_FORM_NEG_*_EMPTY`, `TC_FORM_NEG_*_MALFORMED` | 30 | Positive submit, empty submit, SQL injection |
| **Tier 2: Navigation** | `TC_NAV_*` | 15 | Anchor tag routing, SPA navigation |
| **Tier 3: Interactivity** | `TC_INTERACT_*` | 10 | Button clicks, modal triggers, DOM mutations |
| **Tier 4: Dropdowns** | `TC_SELECT_*` | 10 | `<select>` value change validation |
| **Tier 5: Textareas** | `TC_TEXTAREA_*` | 5 | Multi-line input, special character handling |
| **Tier 6: Accessibility** | `TC_A11Y_*` | 1 | Alt text, aria-labels, keyboard focusability |

**Key Functions:**

| Function | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| [generate_scenarios(dom_data)](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/02_scenario_generator/rule_engine.py#11-237) | Creates scenario list from parsed DOM |
| [save_scenarios(scenarios, run_id)](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/02_scenario_generator/rule_engine.py#238-244) | Persists to `data/{run_id}_scenarios.json` |

**Deduplication Logic:**
- Forms: deduplicated by `selector_guess`
- Navigation: deduplicated by both raw `href` AND resolved URL via `urljoin`
- Filters out: `#` anchors, `mailto:`, `tel:`, `javascript:void`, social media links

### Integration Engine ([integration_engine.py](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/02_scenario_generator/integration_engine.py) — 73 lines)

**Class:** [IntegrationEngine](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/02_scenario_generator/integration_engine.py#5-69)

Pre-defines **26 core test cases** for `automationexercise.com` (Register, Login, Cart, Checkout, etc.). Only injects if the target domain matches.

| Function | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| [inject_core_scenarios(existing, target_url)](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/02_scenario_generator/integration_engine.py#43-69) | Conditionally merges 26 core TCs; marks with `is_core: True` |

