## 15. Module 11 — Regression Optimizer

> **File:** [modules/11_regression_optimizer/optimizer.py](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/11_regression_optimizer/optimizer.py) — 98 lines

**Class:** [RegressionOptimizer](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/modules/11_regression_optimizer/optimizer.py#5-97)

### Deterministic Pruning Algorithm

Analyzes the **3 most recent** historical runs to identify "deeply stable" modules (zero failures, 5+ passes).

| Priority | Deeply Stable Module | Action |
|----------|---------------------|--------|
| **HIGH** | Any | **NEVER pruned** |
| **MEDIUM** | Yes | Keep every 3rd test as canary |
| **LOW** | Yes | **Prune entirely** |
| Any | No (has recent failures) | **Keep** |

> **Key Design Decision:** Uses a deterministic counter (`medium_counter % 3`) instead of `random.random()` for CI/CD reproducibility.

