## 16. Agent Orchestrator

> **File:** [agent/agent_runner.py](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/agent/agent_runner.py) — 441 lines

### Two Execution Modes

| Mode | CLI Flag | Behavior |
|------|----------|----------|
| **Single URL** | `--url "https://..."` | Crawls one URL → one run |
| **Multi-URL Swarm** | `--urls "url1,url2,url3"` | Crawls N URLs sequentially → ONE unified run with all scenarios combined |

### Key CLI Arguments

| Argument | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `--url` | Single target URL |
| `--urls` | Comma-separated multiple URLs |
| `--auto-approve` | Bypass human-in-the-loop approval |
| `--max-scenarios` | Limit auto-approved scenario count |

### Multi-URL Deduplication

When crawling multiple URLs, duplicate `test_id` values get suffixed: `TC_FORM_POS_1` → `TC_FORM_POS_1_v2`.

