## 18. Cypress Configuration

> **File:** [cypress.config.js](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/cypress.config.js) — 100 lines

### Custom Event Hooks

| Hook | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `before:browser:launch` | Removes `--enable-automation` flag, adds `--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled` to bypass bot detection |
| `after:spec` | Writes per-spec status JSON with **error classification** |
| `task.saveDomData` | Writes DOM extraction JSON to disk |

### Error Classification Engine

The `after:spec` hook classifies errors into 7 categories:

| Error Type | Detection Pattern |
|-----------|------------------|
| `TIMEOUT` | "timeout", "timed out" |
| `ELEMENT_NOT_FOUND` | "not found", "could not find" |
| `DETACHED_DOM` | "detached", "stale" |
| `ASSERTION_FAILURE` | "assert", "expected" |
| `SYNTAX_ERROR` | "syntax", "unexpected token" |
| `NAVIGATION_FAILURE` | "navigation", "url" |
| `UNKNOWN` | Everything else |

