## 20. CI/CD Pipeline

> **File:** [.github/workflows/qa-agent-ci.yml](file:///d:/Final%20Project/MASTER%20QA%20AGENT/.github/workflows/qa-agent-ci.yml) — 87 lines

### Triggers

| Trigger | Condition |
|---------|-----------|
| Push | `main` or `develop` branches |
| Pull Request | Against `main` |
| Schedule | Nightly at midnight UTC (`0 0 * * *`) |
| Manual Dispatch | Custom URL + auto-approve toggle |

### Pipeline Steps

1. **Checkout** → `actions/checkout@v3`
2. **Setup Node.js 18** → `actions/setup-node@v3`
3. **Setup Python 3.10** → `actions/setup-python@v4`
4. **Install Python deps** + spaCy model
5. **Install npm deps** (Cypress)
6. **Run agent** in background → auto-approve if CI mode
7. **Upload artifacts** (results, visual diffs, approvals) with 7-day retention

